			<div class="comment-content">
				<p>If all stationary facilities (runways, harbors, fuel depots, radar) will be hit in the opening salvos does that increase the argument for mobile platforms (detection, SAMs, drones and submarines) to constitute the bulk of forces?</p>
<p>Could a realistic number of mobile platforms change the tactical balance away from a first strike?</p>
			</div><!-- .comment-content -->

